message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm pleased with the service I have been receiving so far.
That's great to hear! Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course, my full name is Sarah Thompson.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. Can you now provide me with your date of birth?
Sure, my date of birth is 10/08/1985.
Great, thank you. Lastly, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
My address is 123 Oak Street, London, L1 2AB.
Thank you for completing security. How can I assist you further today, Sarah?
I actually have a concern about my recent claim. It hasn't been resolved yet.
I'm deeply sorry to hear that, Sarah. Let's see how we can help. A possible resolution could be escalating your claim to a senior team member for further assistance. Does this work for you?
That sounds like a good idea. Please proceed with escalating the claim. I appreciate your help, Chris.
I'm glad we could help, Sarah. Your claim will be escalated, and you will receive an update soon. Thank you for reaching out to us today.
